-> Virtual DOM, Fibre and reconcilitation
    - createRoot : this will create it's own root (this is call react tree which will be different from browser tree)
    - Article on react Fiber: https://github.com/acdlite/react-fiber-architecture
    - Features of react fibers:
        - Abitlity to pause, abort, or reuse work as new updates come in; the abitlity to assign priority to different typs of updates.
    -  Reconciliation is the algorithm behind what is popularly understood as the "virtual DOM.


